</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="487" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1004,1859]" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1760,1786]" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Ariyama, 2021" authorityName="Ariyama" authorityYear="2021" box="[322,426,1760,1786]" class="Malacostraca" family="Ochlesidae" genus="Metodius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="487" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis box="[322,426,1760,1786]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">Metodius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[433,537,1760,1786]" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[433,537,1760,1786]" pageId="2" pageNumber="487" rank="genus">gen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
differs from the other odiid genera in the short maxilla 1 palp with rounded bare tip and the large gnathopod 2 propodus almost the same length as the coxa 2.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
